ActNational Battlefields at Quebec Act, 1914
PrecisReappointment of JEAN PIERRE ROBERT of Québec, Quebec, as a Commissioner of the National Battlefields Commission, to hold office during pleasure for a term of four years, effective June 6, 2023; and his designation as chairman of the National Battlefields Commission, to hold office during pleasure for a term of four years, effective June 6, 2023.
